title: New: Woodes – Run For It
body:
With an EP towards the end of last year signalling her star potential, Melbourne’s **Woodes** is back with a grandiose offering in the form of new single, _Run For It_.

Ambitious and anthemic, there’s elements of Lorde and Aurora to the radio ready choruses and slick, impeccable production. Check it out below.
